00:35:44.510 --> 00:35:47.390
As the force that carries
the vibrations from the front

00:35:47.390 --> 00:35:49.660
of the instrument to the
back of the instrument,

00:35:49.660 --> 00:35:54.070
even a half of a millimeter
adjustment can dramatically change

00:35:54.070 --> 00:35:55.910
the sound of this instrument.

00:35:55.910 --> 00:36:02.100
So I know like my luthier will go
in there with a little tool and tap

00:36:02.100 --> 00:36:06.570
