a pretty interesting effect.

00:36:15.330 --> 00:36:20.410
I do know that this instrument
responds very differently

00:36:20.410 --> 00:36:22.830
than anything I've
ever played before.

00:36:22.830 --> 00:36:26.520
So I do think that there is
something to be said about that.

